video:video.video:description: In the continuation of the previous episode we’ll see Chaor’s invasion to the Overworld Arsenal in Kiru City.

video:video.video:title: Time's Up | Chaotic Online
video:video.video:description: In this episode we’ll have a grayish, silent, “Futuresight” with a small and subtle spoiler of the Season’s apex.

video:video.video:title: Gigantempopolis | Chaotic Online
video:video.video:description: In this episode we’ll meet Gigantempopolis, a desert place, full of mysteries, treasures and, of course, curses, in the best The Lord of the Rings style.

video:video.video:title: War Beasts | Chaotic Online
video:video.video:description: In this episode, after a while without mess with other players, Krystella and Klay set up for Peyton to get the scan of a War Beast, a humongous Mipedian titan as powerful as lunatic and, apparently, uncontrollable.

video:video.video:title: From the Deep (Part 1) | Chaotic Online
video:video.video:description: In this episode, a mysterious Creature from a long forgotten past arises again with astonishing and disturbing revelations about the future of Perim.

video:video.video:title: From the Deep (Part 2) | Chaotic Online
video:video.video:description: In the continuation of the previous episode, betrayal, brainwash, a military coup and the beginning of the end… Let the Invasion begin!

video:video.video:title: Tale of Two Toms | Chaotic Online
video:video.video:description: In this episode an easy-going version of our protagonist comes into play and, thanks to an evil pushing, ends up in a fight, in the best Chaotic style.

video:video.video:title: Blight Fight | Chaotic Online
video:video.video:description: In this episode we’ll meet Garv, the OverWorld Caretaker in charge of Lake Morn, helping Tom (and Smildon) to heal the Prexxor Chasm from the Blight instead of fighting it by brute-force.

video:video.video:title: Newbie | Chaotic Online
video:video.video:description: In this episode we’ll meet Shinwan, a newcomer headstrong enough to be the first in Chaotic to get a M&rsquo;arrillian scan.

video:video.video:title: Putting the Muge in Mugic | Chaotic Online
video:video.video:description: In this episode we’ll have a common (and unnecessary) territorial war complete with treason, sabotage, counter-espionage and lessons of leadership between OverWorlders and Mipedians.

video:video.video:title: Mister E | Chaotic Online
video:video.video:description: In this episode we’ll see more about the power of the M&rsquo;arrillians and the beginning of one of the possible futures shown in “Time’s Up”.

video:video.video:title: When a CodeMaster Calls | Chaotic Online
video:video.video:description: In this episode we’ll see Peyton going on a journey into M&rsquo;arrillian territory in name of CodeMaster Hotekk in order to become his apprentice… said no one ever.

video:video.video:title: Earth to Kaz | Chaotic Online
video:video.video:description: In this episode we’ll see Kaz’s passion for Chaotic becoming a problem for him when he needs to prove to the psychologist of his school that Chaotic is a real place o.O

video:video.video:title: Raznus Returns | Chaotic Online
video:video.video:description: In this episode, a problematic excavation leads some Mandiblors led by Odu-Bathax and Raznus, former OverWorld Ambassador to the Danians, now Assimilated, to the basement of the Arsenal of OverWorld.

video:video.video:title: Warriors of Eternity | Chaotic Online
video:video.video:description: In this episode, Sarah is attacked by a Mipedian ghost and her friends, while searching for her, join a group of Mipedians who are searching for the legendary Owayki and his Stone Warriors, immune to the M&rsquo;arrillian’s mind control.

video:video.video:title: UnderWorld Overthrown | Chaotic Online
video:video.video:description: In this episode we’ll see Chaor and his loyal fighters execute a battle plan against the M&rsquo;arrillians in the Marsh of Murk.

video:video.video:title: Triple Threat | Chaotic Online
video:video.video:description: In this episode we’ll see the Tribal Alliance overcoming its cultural differences so they united may have a chance against the M&rsquo;arrillians.

video:video.video:title: Last Stand (Part 1) | Chaotic Online
video:video.video:description: In this episode, the beginning of the end… the battle for Perim is now!

video:video.video:title: Last Stand (Part 2) | Chaotic Online
video:video.video:description: In this episode, the battle continues in different regions of Perim at once… and in the Tribal Alliance itself as well.

video:video.video:title: Legions of Aa'une (Season Finale) | Chaotic Online
video:video.video:description: In this episode, the battle continues with overturns and some shifting… and the end!

video:video.video:title: Perithon! | Chaotic Online
video:video.video:description: In this episode, after an intense battle and glorious victory over the M&rsquo;arrillians, the Tribes decide to keep Tribal Alliance towards a prosperous Perim and, to celebrate the peace, they make a car race… but old habits die hard…

video:video.video:title: Worlds Apart | Chaotic Online
video:video.video:description: In this episode we’ll meet Jycella, Krystella’s twin sister, and we’ll see that the bad relationship between them, common among humans, also happens in Perim, with the twin sisters Aivenna and Nivenna.

video:video.video:title: Kickin' Bot | Chaotic Online
video:video.video:description: In this episode, Perim’s Dr. Frankenstein decides to implement part of his own brain in the Gigantroopers, making them intelligent enough to try to take over the Underworld, resulting in a battle in the best Pacific Rim style.

video:video.video:title: Hotekk's Challenge (Part 1) | Chaotic Online
video:video.video:description: In this episode, Tom wins the seventh battle in the Hotekk Drome, and thus is challenged by the CodeMaster himself.

video:video.video:title: Hotekk's Challenge (Parte 2) | Chaotic Online
video:video.video:description: In this episode, after winning CodeMaster Hotekk in a very intelligent way, Tom gets very disappointed with his reward… until he and his friends discover that a desert and not very interesting Location is actually much more than it looks (really!)

video:video.video:title: Yesterday's Heroes | Chaotic Online
video:video.video:description: In this episode we’ll meet Vlar, a thief renegade by the OverWorld Tribe of Ancient Perim which, possibly, is Maxxor ancestor.

video:video.video:title: Losers' Circle | Chaotic Online
video:video.video:description: In this episode, Kaz is so psyched with his new scans from ancient Perim he decides to challenge every player who defeated him, thinking nobody would stand a chance… until his archenemy proves him otherwise.

video:video.video:title: A Gigantic Mission | Chaotic Online
video:video.video:description: In this episode we’ll see Vlar guiding Kiru and his fighters through the Temple of the ancient Gigantempopolis, when the giants were alive, in an attempt of dissuading Kaal to not invade Kiru City anymore, however, during the trip, the own future of the OverWorld was traced.

video:video.video:title: Threshold of Destruction | Chaotic Online
video:video.video:description: In this episode, once Dranakis Threshold’s secret leaked out, several players ported to ancient Perim, including Chaotic’s “Bonnie &amp; Clyde”, who didn’t take long in conspiring with an old acquaintance, making of a painful event become, potentially, irreversible.

video:video.video:title: A Peytonic Adventure | Chaotic Online
video:video.video:description: In this episode, an adventure in the 007 style in which Peyton is challenged by a world famous art counterfeiter for a Chaotic match.

video:video.video:title: Elementary | Chaotic Online
video:video.video:description: In this episode we’ll meet the four Elemental Servants of the Lost City and a battle in Chaotic with them all at once.

video:video.video:title: Son of the Spiritlands | Chaotic Online
video:video.video:description: In this episode, an indestructible Creature from the Spiritlands threatens to destroy the whole Perim unless Tangath Toborn faces him.
